text: The University of Rennes 2 - Upper Brittany is a national university in France. It is located in the city of Rennes. It was created in 1969. == Faculties == They are 5 faculties: *Faculty of foreign languages *Faculty of social sciences *Faculty of Human sciences *Faculty of Arts, Humanities, and communication *Faculty of sports. == Other websites == *official website Category:Colleges and universities in France Category:Rennes Category:1969 establishments in France
title: Rennes 2 University
